USA: AMEX closing averages.AMEX closing averages.Prices on the American Stock Exchange closed higher Tuesday in heavy trading.The Amex index closed at 559.29, up 1.69.Gainers beat losers 291 to 217.The average price per share rose $0.04.Preliminary volume was 22,814,210, compared with 16,413,225 Monday.(Prices official as of 1645 EDT/2045 GMT)